return function(self, player, prevState) if not self.panning and prevState == self.STATE_IDLE and love.keyboard.isDown("right") then self.panning = true self.scene:run(BlockPlayer { Ease(self.scene.camPos, "x", -800, 0.3), Wait(2), Ease(self.scene.camPos, "x", 0, 0.3), Do(function() self.panning = false end) }) end end
